{"word":"H4801 - מֶרְחָק - merchâq - mer-khawk' - Far","slug":"H4801","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מֶרְחָק</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>merchâq"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mer-khawk'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Far"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E8;&#x05D7;&#x05E7; - mercha&#x0302;q</b> - <i>mer-khawk'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H7368\">H7368</a>; <i>remoteness</i>, that is, (concretely) a <i>distant</i> place; often (adverbially) <i>from afar</i>: -  (a, dwell in, very) far (country, off). See also <a href=\"#/H1023\">H1023</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7350\">H7350</a>, <a href=\"#/H7368\">H7368</a>, <a href=\"#/H7369\">H7369</a>"}]}